data.description: Complete Rennovation. Located in Hart Cty just minutes to Lake Hartwell is a craftsman home in the middle of being completely remodeled down to the studs. Once completed this newer home will provide luxury vinyl flooring, decorator paint colors, decorative lighting package, tile baths, & upgraded hardware. This flowing, open floorplan will boast a gracious sized living room open to the breakfast room & designer kitchen complete w/ granite countertops, custom cabinetry, & stainless steel appliances. The bedrooms can be found just up the stairs & each will host lush carpet flooring, ceiling fan light fixtures, & direct access to one of the perfectly appointed full baths. Additional flex space will be available in the unfinished basement ready for completion.
